          "body": {
            "labels": [
              { "label": "Design System" }
            ],
            "content": {
              "callout": "Figma's Simple Design System",
              "supplements": [
                {
                    "text": "I was fortunate to be asked to build Figma's first public-facing UI Kit, which is integrated into the assets panel of the product. I was responsible for creating a best-practice approach that could potentially be used by millions of designers worldwide. The launch was also a partnership first, with Apple and Google's Material Design being shipped as UI Kits too; alongside Simple Design System.",
                    "links": []
                  },
                {
                  "text": "Role: Solo designer on Figma's first ever in-product design system.",
                  "links": []
                },
                {
                    "text": "Collaborators: For launch, Jake Albaugh built the code, Jacob Miller was product manager, Zoe Adelman was project manager.",
                    "links": []
                  },
                {
                    "text": "Users: ~18 thousand.",
                    "links": []
                  },
                {
                  "text": "Usage: 4 million component inserts in 30 days.",
                  "links": []
                },
                {
                    "text": "Timeline: February 2024 start, launched June 2024. Maintenance and component additions are ongoing, logged via public Asana form.",
                    "links": [
                        {
                            "word": "Asana",
                            "href": "https://form.asana.com/?k=wcWtx3xQsHp26re5PZLkwQ&d=10497086658021"
                        }
                    ]
                },                
                {
                  "text": "Launch: Released as part of the official 2024 keynote at Figma's annual conference, Config. This was launched alongside brand new UI kits from Apple and Google, another company first.",
                  "links": [
                    {
                      "word": "Config",
                      "href": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n5gJgkO2Dg0&t=879s"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "buttons": [
                {
                  "text": "Take a look",
                  "href": "https://www.figma.com/community/file/1005505895825202287/responsive-handoff-components"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
